title: About GDG Tacna
description: Google Developer Groups (GDG) Tacna is a community of developers passionate about technology and innovation. We gather to learn, share knowledge, and create solutions that positively impact our region.
ourMission: To foster technological development in Tacna through collaborative learning, innovation, and knowledge sharing about Google technologies and other emerging platforms.
ourVision: To be the most influential tech community in the region, training world-class developers who contribute to Peru's digital growth.
joinUsDescription: Be part of a vibrant community of developers. Participate in events, workshops, and projects that will help you grow professionally.
